00:34:03,600 --> 00:34:06,363
And so we actually ended up adding a safety mechanism

697
00:34:06,403 --> 00:34:07,704
that you don't just have to tap a button

698
00:34:07,724 --> 00:34:08,684
to dismantle your gear in Destiny.

